Look at this component. What does the user see on screen?

```jsx
function PriceTag() {
  const basePrice = 50;
  const discount = 0.2;
  const finalPrice = basePrice * (1 - discount);

  return (
    <div className="price-tag">
      <p className="original">${basePrice}</p>
      <p className="sale">${finalPrice}</p>
    </div>
  );
}
```

